sentences: Nicole A. Avant (born March 6, 1968) is a former United States Ambassador to the Bahamas from 2009 to 2011.
Nicole A. Avant (born March 6, 1968) is a former United States Ambassador to the Bahamas from 2009 to 2011.
Nicole Avant graduated in 1986 from Beverly Hills High School and in 1990 from the California State University, Northridge with a B.A. in communications.
